坏，股骨头坏死发生率很高，多采用人工关节置换术治疗。（3）由于误诊、漏诊，或治疗方法不当，导致股骨颈陈旧骨折不愈合,影响功能的畸形愈合，股骨头缺血坏死,关节面塌陷导致髖关节骨关节炎疼痛跛行的，应采用手术方法治疗。</span></p>","topic":null,"options":[{"id":6806,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 10:40:19","updateTime":"2019-06-20 10:40:19","isTrue":false,"questionId":2505,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">左下肢骨牵引</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":6807,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 10:40:19","updateTime":"2019-06-20 10:40:19","isTrue":false,"questionId":2505,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">药物治疗</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":6808,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 10:40:19","updateTime":"2019-06-20 10:40:19","isTrue":false,"questionId":2505,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">左下肢皮牵引</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":6809,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 10:40:19","updateTime":"2019-06-20 10:40:19","isTrue":false,"questionId":2505,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">髋部石膏固定</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0},{"id":6810,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-20 10:40:19","updateTime":"2019-06-20 10:40:19","isTrue":true,"questionId":2505,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:楷体\">尽早手术治疗</span></span></p>","selectCnt":0}],"tags":[{"id":967,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-09 11:34:52","updateTime":"2019-06-09 11:34:52","name":"运动A3","questionCnt":11,"tagTypeId":47},{"id":927,"delFlag":false,"createTime":"2019-06-09 11:27:22","updateTime":"2019-06-09 11:27:22","name":"181","questionCnt":150,"tagTypeId":46}],"hasCollect":false,"userAnswer":null,"questionPath":null},{"id":2502,"createTime":"2019-06-20 10:38:27","topicId":null,"tagId":927,"rule":1,"weight":1,"sort":111,"accuracy":0.0,"content":"<p><span style=\";font-family:楷体;font-size:16px\"><span style